      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i hear you, but it’s not just 'noise'. it’s everything. it’s my phone, it’s my classmates, it’s even people i thought were friends. it feels like no matter what i do, i’m just the target. i look at the future and i don't see anything good, just more of this. it’s like i’m trapped in a room with everyone hating me and there’s no door. i just want the noise to finally shut up. i just want everything to stop.",
